title: Layla asks: What if a cat, a weasel, and a dragon teamed up to save the world?
description:
Cthunkle is back and trying to invade the real world via a carnival at Drew’s house. But can a What If World story even happen on What Is World? Find out for yourself!

This episode originally aired July 17, 2017.

Join our Patreon for Ad-Free stories, a Shout-Out on the show, bonus audio, a better chance of having your question answered, and more! patreon.com/whatifworld
